"For example, ТЇ1 defines the absolute value function.\n"
"\n"
"## Friends and relatives\n"
"\n"
"* If you have ТЇ2 as an assumption, you can use\n"
"ТЇ3 to reduce the expression ТЇ4 to ТЇ5.\n"
"* If you have ТЇ6 as an assumption, you can use\n"
"ТЇ7 to reduce the expression ТЇ8 to ТЇ9."
