#. ТЇ8: `тЂ B т C`
#. ТЇ9: `A = Bт = Bт = Bт тІ = C`
#. ТЇ10: `calc`
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"With ТЇ0, you insert an intermediate step into an equation or equivalence.\n"
"\n"
"| before | tactic    | after                |\n"
"|:------------ |:--------- |:----------------------- |\n"
"| ТЇ1    | ТЇ2 | ТЇ3 and ТЇ4 |\n"
"| ТЇ5    | ТЇ6 | ТЇ7 and ТЇ8 |\n"
"\n"
"Since you can repeat the tactic several times, it is suitable for\n"
"performing a тcalculationт ТЇ9 step by step.\n"
"\n"
"(Outside of the game, however, the multi-line tactic ТЇ10 is better suited "
"for such calculations.)"
msgstr ""
"Mit ТЇ0 fУМgst du in eine Gleichung oder Уquivalenz einen Zwischenschritt "
"ein.\n"
"\n"
"| vorher       | Taktik    | nachher                | \n"
"|:------------ |:--------- |:-----------------------| \n"
"| ТЇ1           | ТЇ2        | ТЇ3 und ТЇ4              | \n"
"| ТЇ5           | ТЇ6        | ТЇ7 und ТЇ8              | \n"
"\n"
"Da du die Taktik mehrmals wiederholen kannst, ist sie geeignet, um Schritt "
"fУМr Schritt eine тRechnungт ТЇ9 durchzufУМhren.\n"
"\n"
"(AuУerhalb vom Spiel ist allerdings die mehrzeilige Taktik ТЇ10 besser fУМr "
"derartige Rechnungen geeignet.)"

#. ТЇ0: `suffices h : P`
